Alias      MyAntiD0     anti-D0
ChargeConj MyD0         MyAntiD0
#
Alias      MyD*-        D*-
Alias      MyD*+        D*+
ChargeConj MyD*-        MyD*+
#
Alias      MyD_s1+         D_s1+
Alias      MyD_s1-         D_s1-
ChargeConj MyD_s1+         MyD_s1-
#
Alias      MyD_s0*+         D_s0*+
Alias      MyD_s0*-         D_s0*-
