Decay B_s0sig
0.0070   MyD'_s1-   mu+    nu_mu        PHOTOS  ISGW2;
0.0070   MyD_s2*-   mu+    nu_mu        PHOTOS  ISGW2;
Enddecay
CDecay anti-B_s0sig


Decay MyD'_s1-
